{"tid":960144,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［權威］2018年英雄電影排行榜","createTime":"2018-12-29T07:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T03:56:02.000Z","uid":86587,"like":7,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e2253892ead65e452da1af9e85b94bae9c151888","tid":960144,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"第6名  Ant-Man 2<br />\n成套戲零笑位，打鬥零創意，電影質素堪比雷神2，唯一值得睇嘅就係片尾彩蛋，為Avengers 4鋪路<br />\n<img src=\"https://static1.srcdn.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Ant-Man-and-the-Wasp-and-Ghost-Ending-Explained.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.srcdn.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FAnt-Man-and-the-Wasp-and-Ghost-Ending-Explained.jpg&h=977ea6be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第5名 Aquaman，黑豹<br />\n兩套戲故事相似，Aquaman贏在CG同Amber Heard對波，黑豹贏在反派，所以打和喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.thr.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/NFE_portrait/2017/05/aquaman_mera.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.thr.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2FNFE_portrait%2F2017%2F05%2Faquaman_mera.jpg&h=2d85404f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pmcvariety.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/avengers-infinity-war-9.jpg?w=700&amp;h=393&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpmcvariety.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F04%2Favengers-infinity-war-9.jpg%3Fw%3D700%26h%3D393%26crop%3D1&h=cabf4112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第4名 Deadpool 2<br />\n繼續惡搞Marvel DC，但係黔驢技窮玩唔出咩新花樣，希望下集Avengers嘅加入可以帶來新鮮感<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hindustantimes.com/rf/image_size_960x540/HT/p2/2018/05/18/Pictures/_5b0de432-5a8c-11e8-b431-73159b4b09e2.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Frf%2Fimage_size_960x540%2FHT%2Fp2%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2FPictures%2F_5b0de432-5a8c-11e8-b431-73159b4b09e2.PNG&h=2cde1dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3名 Venom<br />\n雖然影評劣評如潮，但係主角同Venom之間嘅基情互動寫得幾好，亦都唔會懶有深度夾硬講啲咩大道理，可見Sony好清楚觀眾入場想睇啲咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qwfxWHEdLZavZLBipGSxaaqNTCA=/0x0:1200x800/1820x1213/filters:focal(533x447:725x639):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/61649917/venom.0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FqwfxWHEdLZavZLBipGSxaaqNTCA%3D%2F0x0%3A1200x800%2F1820x1213%2Ffilters%3Afocal%28533x447%3A725x639%29%3Aformat%28webp%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F61649917%2Fvenom.0.jpeg&h=54739e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2名 Teen Titans Go! To the Movies<br />\n套戲比起Deadpool更無厘頭，更加惡搞，證明DC都係拍番動畫電影算喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjM3NDMwMDE2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ1Mjg5NTM@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BMjM3NDMwMDE2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ1Mjg5NTM%40._V1_.jpg&h=8b37bbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第1名 Avengers 3<br />\n無需多講<br />\n<img src=\"https://cnet2.cbsistatic.com/img/UBjs76aKTzgolzX4LPmhjuesXIY=/1600x900/2018/05/09/184a5e8a-b6df-434d-a02a-c921d64b8dab/scua6kiby05vfqzbobfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnet2.cbsistatic.com%2Fimg%2FUBjs76aKTzgolzX4LPmhjuesXIY%3D%2F1600x900%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F184a5e8a-b6df-434d-a02a-c921d64b8dab%2Fscua6kiby05vfqzbobfu.jpg&h=d5cb55a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  G持樓主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  垃圾排名，收皮喇"},{"pid":"1dd3f24cf6c8f5d988fa87c5ab406eea80316181","tid":960144,"uid":215373,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"水行俠第三，蜘蛛俠平行宇宙第二"},{"pid":"f3be3e0557cf9e84794cbdc2969ddb36d150e48f","tid":960144,"uid":64374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e023d0126982d327cc80bc5cba3156c102787a30","tid":960144,"uid":60288,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"Antman點會成套戲零笑位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nblack panther就零笑位<br />\n<br />\n我排<br />\n1.Avengers3<br />\n2.Antman2<br />\n3.Aquaman<br />\n4.Deadpool2<br />\n5.Venom<br />\n6.Black Panther"},{"pid":"bb176c885508a5d82a232f137a354ef9e19513fd","tid":960144,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"負評 毋須多講"},{"pid":"94a6b7c5fee54dad763080b62b0f5c6c30e45a1f","tid":960144,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c872f1e2727f66b03ead10c39e5028e833f464b","tid":960144,"uid":195438,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1dd3f24cf6c8f5d988fa87c5ab406eea80316181","tid":960144,"uid":215373,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"水行俠第三，蜘蛛俠平行宇宙第二"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"認同，年尾呢兩套真係超晒班，諗都冇諗過"},{"pid":"1e26f7c5a17023a1e0a1b2957e28f34fe3caa33c","tid":960144,"uid":215373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c872f1e2727f66b03ead10c39e5028e833f464b","tid":960144,"uid":195438,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1dd3f24cf6c8f5d988fa87c5ab406eea80316181","tid":960144,"uid":215373,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"水行俠第三，蜘蛛俠平行宇宙第二"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"認同，年尾呢兩套真係超晒班，諗都冇諗過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T07:53:37.000Z","msg":"樓主亂咁排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100bf41cfcb1658756a9b515a0e1a99fd5e2660f","tid":960144,"uid":159183,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"個人感受 不喜勿插<br />\n水行俠<br />\navg3<br />\n死侍2<br />\n黑豹<br />\n毒魔<br />\n蟻俠2"},{"pid":"05c501c3500c48e5f72f24ff8f9068b8f8b0c753","tid":960144,"uid":119330,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"Teen Titans Go! To the Movies 無睇過 就唔落評語<br />\n<br />\n真係要排<br />\n1. A3<br />\n2. Aquaman<br />\n3. DP2<br />\n4. Antman2<br />\n5. Venom<br />\n6. 黑豹<br />\n<br />\n6. 黑豹動作場面設定 個人唔太欣賞 <br />\n尤其是最終大戰 兩個係度一邊打 一邊避火車<br />\n營造唔到最終大戰個緊張感之餘<br />\n亦令動作場面斷斷續續 無連貫<br />\n<br />\n5. Venom整體上唔差 動作場面上亦都係花過心思<br />\n以Venom人設去設計點打<br />\n但問題係CG真係差少少<br />\n好多位都好亂 睇到一頭霧水<br />\n另外 故事亦有bug 不過唔深究會睇得幾開心<br />\n<br />\n4. Antman2 睇主角個老友點鳩UP 真係笑到碌地<br />\n動作場面設計精彩<br />\n尤其是黃蜂女同黑幫班人係廚房度打 真係正到無論<br />\n笑點唔少 故事唔錯<br />\n<br />\n3. DP2 整體上係唔錯 充份發揮&quot;賤&quot;呢個特點<br />\n笑點十足 尤其是自殺跳傘 同 最後回到過去改時間線<br />\n真心覺得勁好笑<br />\n動作場面上 DP 同 cable打以及鋼人同紅坦克打 都好好睇<br />\n<br />\n2. 除左個色調我唔鍾意外 真心唔錯<br />\n尤其是360度鏡頭以及一鏡到底打鬥 真係好新鮮<br />\n<br />\n1. A3最強大之處 係時間控制 每一個英雄都有時間表演<br />\n其他既<br />\n不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cec0995552118f0a76cdfd61d0a44ed38576dbe","tid":960144,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"Aquaman &gt; Avg3 &gt; Antman2 &gt; DP2<br />\n黑豹同毒魔無睇"},{"pid":"b4979b98e9a8700f12e3cb9a98bf83800625dd80","tid":960144,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"影評人： 黑豹世界第一"},{"pid":"c1282101cdce5a5f1a95cb98a4003b52a7172f5b","tid":960144,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"iw&gt; aquaman&gt; 其他"},{"pid":"d63ffb3ae694dd8d046b8de5b5fc1978a9f3debb","tid":960144,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到冇人講spidey"},{"pid":"b6d65f99d2c6d160c662735b03c955e84d627f9b","tid":960144,"uid":149201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d63ffb3ae694dd8d046b8de5b5fc1978a9f3debb","tid":960144,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:05:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到冇人講spidey"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"superhero movie 好多人prefer睇真人版多過動畫電影<br />\n甚至有少少抗拒"},{"pid":"df4d6372e353e4ec838074e3efc2efa8504e2e74","tid":960144,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"avenger 3<br />\nspider-man <br />\naquaman<br />\ndeadpool 2<br />\nantman 2<br />\nblack panther"},{"pid":"e1a532da42531588ce9843991eb2e7065d09dd82","tid":960144,"uid":2162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"個人感覺<br />\navg3/水行俠/Spider-Verse<br />\n今年係呢3套覺得好掂<br />\n最驚喜都係水行俠<br />\n果陣仲笑佢點拍恐怖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSpider 拍出黎真係最好睇既GG俠電影<br />\n都係驚喜之作<br />\n<br />\n毒魔<br />\n蟻俠2<br />\n死待2<br />\n蟻俠同死待個人覺得仲衰過第一集<br />\n<br />\n黑豹<br />\n係ca3 果陣d 動作場面仲好睇過佢套戲<br />\n唔係Killmonger 撐場真係唔掂"},{"pid":"8eeca3d5dc4efbda1422ffa2640e02261c21a38b","tid":960144,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"Into the Spider-Verse&gt; all"},{"pid":"9c216fdbe8c4e1d08542e808c92bd56942009c01","tid":960144,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec192bab224343a0cbcc3355e33a3e72964f857","tid":960144,"uid":159183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:35:26.000Z","msg":"今年呢兩場大戰都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBs64mo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBs64mo.gif&h=89ee710b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJcrjUK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu